title: Beauty.and.the.Geek.AU.s06e04.WebRip.Hector.mp4
description:
Please Note- This is more of a web capture than a rip. It was done by using a Hauppauge recorder to record it from the 7Plus site.
I cannot do a webrip from there because it is encrypted. The picture is a little bit stilted throughout it and there is not much I could do about that. The reason I missed the actual cap was because I was rushed to hospital to have another heart operation. I am posting this because I cannot see an alternative cap anywhere and I am also still in hospital and this episode does not appear to be repeated on TV.
I have also had multiple requests for it too! It is not awful lol! It is just not the best ever!
